'''''Kada River''''' ni filime yikinamico yo muri [[Nigeriya]] yo muri 2017 iyobowe na Toka McBaror ari nawe wayifatanije na Forinclay Ejeh hamwe nubuyobozi bwakozwe na Olakunle Churchill . <ref name="Pre">https://xplorenollywood.com/toka-mcbarors-kada-river-makes-opening-film-at-the-nollywood-travel-festival/</ref> Muri iyi filime hagaragaramo abakinnyi ba Nollywood n'abakinnyi nka Joke Silva, Keppy Ekpenyong, Rachel Oniga and Bayray McNwizu . Abandi barimo uwahoze ari murugo muri Big Brother Naija 2017 - TBoss (Tokunbo Badmus), <ref>https://www.nigeriafilms.com/movie-news/85-film-tv-workshop/46407-tboss-first-nollywood-movie-with-eniola-badmus-photos</ref> Umukinnyi wa filime wo muri Gana - Fella Makafui, Chris Okagbue, James Blessing, Rakiya Attah and Oluchi Madubuko. <ref>https://www.pulse.ng/entertainment/movies/kada-river-rachael-oniga-bayray-mcnwizu-olakunle-churchill-attend-press-conference/mp3zpd3</ref> <ref>https://www.pulse.ng/entertainment/movies/tboss-reality-tv-star-makes-acting-debut-in-kada-river/9egf43w</ref> <ref name="To">https://m.guardian.ng/saturday-magazine/a-huge-world-premiere-for-toka-mcbarors-kada-river-in-toronto/</ref> Iyi filime ni epic yerekana ibibazo byugarije Leta ya Kaduna, inyito ikaba irindi zina ry'Umugezi wa Kaduna . <ref name="BC">https://thenationonlineng.net/big-church-foundation-unveils-kada-river/</ref>

== Umusaruro ==
Iyi filime yafatiwe hafi ya Kafanchan na Kagoro, ahabereye ubuzima nyabwo bwabereye ku ya 21 Gashyantare 2000 nkuko byavuzwe n'umuyobozi. <ref name="X">https://janellesnollywooddiary.com/kada-river-movie-review/</ref> Umusaruro wacyo watewe inkunga na Big Church Foundation.  <ref name="BC" />

== Umugambi ==
Iyi filime yerekana ubushyamirane bwa kera hagati ya Boduas na Shawlains, bwarangije imvururu zikaze kandi ziva amaraso, hagati aho abakunzi babiri bato, Jerome ( Chris Okagbue ) na Nadia ( Fella Makafui ), baharanira gufasha guhindura urwango rukabije. kurera hagati y'amoko yabo.  <ref>https://www.nollywoodreinvented.com/2017/05/coming-soon-kada-river.html</ref> 

